        "text_snippet": "The methylation of mixed TriMB was also investigated. The proportion of 1,2,4-TriMB, 1,3,5-TriMB, and 1,2,3-TriMB in the feed was set at a ratio of 62:30:8 in accordance with the thermodynamic equilibrium... Mixed TriMB conversion was higher than weighted 1,2,4-TriMB conversion.",
